cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper deals with the development of artificial general intelligence, specifically in the context of evolving neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses techniques for reducing catastrophic forgetting, which is a common problem in machine learning, suggesting that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper focuses on reinforcement learning tasks, which could place it in cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
